---
title: Chicken Souvlaki Dinner  with Dilly Rice and Creamy Feta Sauce
description: Chicken with a hint of bright, lemony flavour teams up perfectly with buttery dill rice and fresh salad. Tangy feta-dill sauce is dolloped on top to round out this meal!
